{"id":8169,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　刚刚收到邮政发行部门通知，本刊明年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月份邮局订阅量比今年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月增长</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，仅邮局这一块订阅量已突破每月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">万册！尽管各地批发、零售及邮购的数字尚未统计上来，也足以确定《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年发行总量大增！<BR></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　炎黄春秋杂志社全体工作人员感谢广大读者朋友对我们的信任、理解和支持！在杂志售价有所提高的情况下，仍然一如既往地关注《炎黄春秋》杂志的发展和进步。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">　　在新的一年里，我们将坚守《炎黄春秋》杂志的办刊方向，为千千万万读者朋友送上一本本独立、真实、权威、厚重的《炎黄春秋》杂志。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>","title":"好消息：《炎黄春秋》杂志2011年订阅量大增！","time":1292954803999}